{"tid":2001513,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"用中國經濟增長速度高黎笑香港就好似用小朋友高得快黎笑姚明咁","createTime":"2020-05-04T14:42:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T15:28:29.000Z","uid":140953,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b6ddaf2f4e7469cbbb11e427303ee19b2536e5ff","tid":2001513,"uid":140953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:42:45.000Z","msg":"其實中國人/藍絲點解講到一個已發展地區經濟增長速度慢過發展中地區係值得笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最興就係用以前香港佔中國GDP四分一定五分一到依家只係幾%黎笑香港廢<br />\n但原來比較過就知中國既所謂高速增長，係發展中地區黎講常見到不得了<br />\n仲要笑一個經濟發展程度係世界頂尖位置既香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n情況就好似拎自己個3歲大既仔黎笑姚明冇得高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(香港好過姚明既係香港經濟仲有得增長)<br />\n<br />\n更唔好講，香港係已發展地區黎講，經濟增長速度都係算快"},{"pid":"c1e323b843fd17921bc4b6a044ad70050c015e29","tid":2001513,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:43:11.000Z","msg":"支那人均GDP vs 香港"},{"pid":"a58bafdb9fd1614b0fea289239777df3f860b6d3","tid":2001513,"uid":312692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1e323b843fd17921bc4b6a044ad70050c015e29","tid":2001513,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:43:11.000Z","msg":"支那人均GDP vs 香港"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲五毛肯定拎北上廣比"},{"pid":"7f1ce43796abd7b2b57533f714a2100b6a043d5f","tid":2001513,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a58bafdb9fd1614b0fea289239777df3f860b6d3","tid":2001513,"uid":312692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1e323b843fd17921bc4b6a044ad70050c015e29","tid":2001513,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:43:11.000Z","msg":"支那人均GDP vs 香港"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲五毛肯定拎北上廣比"},"citedBy":1,"replyTim